{"tid":1867177,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"純白戰袍 - Nike 正式揭露 2020 東京奧運美國隊受獎隊服","createTime":"2020-02-07T05:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T05:31:51.000Z","uid":59114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f6b7f3bc2c1e334d63aac30fdcadf9241dda5cb5","tid":1867177,"uid":59114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fQNEyo1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfQNEyo1.jpg&h=4b11fc34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGGmMJ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGGmMJ1.jpg&h=482896dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n距離 2020 年東京奧運已經剩下約莫半年的時間，負責製作國家隊隊服的品牌們也陸陸續續地揭露今回將讓國家隊披上的戰袍。早先美國國家隊合作夥伴 Nike 就正式公開了為運動員受獎時特別製作的隊服。作為「Medal Stand」系列的一部分，今回 Nike 以純白色調作為主軸，並挪用日本傳統服飾和服的線條在其中，極簡主義的設計僅在胸前和背後標記上 Nike 與「USA」字樣，雖然在外觀上的亮點或許不多，但今次所使用的面料全部為對地球環境友善的環保永續材質，好比對應褲款即是使用百分之百回收尼龍與百分之百的回收聚酯纖維製成，這樣的靈感來自於東京奧運的環保獎牌。服裝之外，Nike 也為運動員們特別製作了一款全新的 Nike VaporMax，搭載 FlyEase 科技的這款 VaporMax 由 75% 製作廢材重製而成，鞋面的 Flyknit 織面亦是使用回收再利用的聚酯纖維。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">source : <a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2020/2/nike-team-usa-medal-stand-vapormax-olympic-collection?utm_term=Autofeed&amp;utm_campaign=facebook_post&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=Facebook&amp;fbclid=IwAR00u4dUyPt7SR5EbhuEJDWCDDvv1hKWktexSsBOwevX_r6DfT2mEf358M4#Echobox=1581051106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2020%2F2%2Fnike-team-usa-medal-stand-vapormax-olympic-collection%3Futm_term%3DAutofeed%26utm_campaign%3Dfacebook_post%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3DFacebook%26fbclid%3DIwAR00u4dUyPt7SR5EbhuEJDWCDDvv1hKWktexSsBOwevX_r6DfT2mEf358M4%23Echobox%3D1581051106&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwW8HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=266d9bbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2020/2/nike-team-usa-medal-stand-vapormax-olympic-collection?utm_term=Autofeed&amp;utm_campaign=facebook_post&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=Facebook&amp;fbclid=IwAR00u4dUyPt7SR5EbhuEJDWCDDvv1hKWktexSsBOwevX_r6DfT2mEf358M4#Echobox=1581051106</a></span><br />\n<br />\n有冇人知中國隊係咪用柒牌做隊服品牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6016c6f4eb0bf31cd73f07ab6761c64b0c443262","tid":1867177,"uid":88982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"搞唔搞得成都未知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}